{"tid":1467684,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"813仲未輸 求下你入嚟睇下","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:29:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T18:14:07.000Z","uid":3173,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b611fd35f67c99155c5558cdde661879d57584ba","tid":1467684,"uid":3173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:29:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">必睇</span><span style=\"font-size: large;\">813「和你非」有感+未來方向</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">深歌P牌仔 寫呢篇文章寫左成差唔多2粒鐘 希望可以比更多兄弟睇到</span><br />\n<br />\n唔轉發 兄弟排得好靚<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">禁入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\nSource:<a href=\"http://lih.kg/khOEPQX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/khOEPQX</a>"},{"pid":"aa11bc788b5de833bf1e0202f5e88bdcfa51f20a","tid":1467684,"uid":3173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:31:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"41fcfa79708abaf40c8b99f70d9e4fa82e183106","tid":1467684,"uid":174541,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:32:33.000Z","msg":"禮貌版<br />\n前線你好！核彈我也不會割。天琦說過與港共鬥爭不能有任何底線。既然有鬼捉不了已成事實(亦得到官方承認)，何不反其道而行，將一切大眾不能接受的行為推卸給popo(注意！並非割！)有了這免死金牌，前線能放下民意顧慮，盡情去做該做的事(不要斷正就可以)。你們的背後有我們！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">誠狠版<br />\n屌你老母，醒少少好唔好?班差佬畀咗咁大 個核彈你都唔識玩?！ 天琦講過你班撚屌唔好有任何潔癖， 咁撚正氣點打中共啲陰招。示威肯定有鬼， 捉嚟都嘥鳩氣。 用下你個豬腦逆向思維咁諗， 有咩事咪奶撚落曬啲臥底到囉。 大眾淨係需要一個合理到嘅版本，陰謀論冇所謂㗎。 拎撚住依個免死金牌， 前線手足咪可以放手做，文宣我哋咪可以輕鬆打囉。 屌你老母，對面元朗嗰時已經做緊謠，唔係唔撚返佢哋呀?</span></span>"},{"pid":"731a8c783eceeb682ded4a7fd324d7f8f41bbf47","tid":1467684,"uid":3173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:34:33.000Z","msg":"比多d人睇到"},{"pid":"8a81608bb4f157386b68f4c5d0b3a46b7ed8578e","tid":1467684,"uid":3173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:34:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4da7eb4bfc8edf1739f356628932697bc6349611","tid":1467684,"uid":3173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:37:55.000Z","msg":"送多大家一句John Lennon 既quote: (連儂牆之父)<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「當抗爭向暴力升級，你便墮入建制的把戲內。當權者會不惜一切地惹怒你，拉扯你的髮鬚，搧你的耳光，引誘你動粗。只要將你迫為暴徒，他們便有方法收拾你。唯一令當權者束手無策的，是非暴力與幽默。」</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"013af7448b11d82f17fb8245da10486b4cf6a212","tid":1467684,"uid":3173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:39:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">大家繼續努力! 香港既未來就喺我地手上!</span></span>"},{"pid":"070f4d6bdaf5f608f2b0c461ad7304ac54c1b13c","tid":1467684,"uid":3173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:42:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8978e719bc3db23a690097a61a8f332302fa9da9","tid":1467684,"uid":3173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:43:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d259b0358ed3f299de45a51af8eb97610dc792c","tid":1467